# Item list view
Display an empty table
Display list of item in the table
Toggle item
Slide to delete
Display add button

# Add item view
Navigate to a new table view when tap add button (Add item view)
Display cancel button
Display done button
Tap cancel or done button go back to item list
Add text input in Add item view
Add focus to text input
Disable done button when text is empty
Disable done button on keyboard when text is empty
Enable clear text button on text input
Add new item into the list

# Edit item
Adjust view, checkmark on the left and display detail disclosure button
Tap to edit
Enable done button
Update item (Delegate)

# Persist Data
Save data (FileManager)
Load data
